original_title: A+: The Personal Trainers Grade Their Top Students
overview: In the finale to the "Personal Trainers" series, Sebastian Bonnet's consummate talents as a taskmaster are on display just as much as theabilities of the freshmen. Sebastian, joined by Dano Sulik and Brandon Manilow, puts a giffed group of studlets through their paces, drilling them over and over until they know how to have white-hot sex on camera. In the end, each of them received a solid "A+" for his performance.
title: A+: The Personal Trainers Grade Their Top Students
